An animated pastel pink stamp with text that reads, "Wash your hands" and an image of hands underneath a stream of water

An animated stamp based on the '98 version of Trigun that switches between the logo and a few scenes. One scene has Vash the Stampede removing empty bullets from his custom revolver, and another scene is a stationary image of Vash
